DBI-Factory

This is a simple factory class for DBI database handle.
Please refer to documentation for the details.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

You need some preparation for using this module.
See documentation for the details.


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc DBI::Factory

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=DBI-Factory

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/DBI-Factory

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/DBI-Factory

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/DBI-Factory/


